Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:10.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,無様だな　生ぬるい環境で正義を気取る
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:13.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,戦場も知らない室内犬どもはよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:16.91,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,全部ぶっ壊す　そのために
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:19.69,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,このクソみたいな世界で生きてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:29.43,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ここまでにしておきますか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:31.69,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,待てよ　まだやれる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:35.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そのような上の空状態ではなにも身につきませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:38.57,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,では　わたしは森を見まわってきます
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.27,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,くそっ　見ぬかれてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,よい…記憶を…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:50.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,気分転換に　収穫祭でも行くか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:22.51,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,却下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:22.51,TEXT-JP-UP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,却下だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:25.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,やっぱり　ダメか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:28.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,え？なんだよ　ちょっとくらいいいじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:29.87,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,仕方ありませんですわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:35.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,はじめてお友たちとお祭りに一緒に行けるかと思ったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:37.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,来年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:41.92,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,来年は　絶対オカ研みんなで収穫祭をまわろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:44.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,静流も　会長も一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,いいねそれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:47.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,うん　すごくいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:50.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そうだな　静流もきっと喜ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:51.19,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:56.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そのときは　My best friend 吉野も引きずって行かないとな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,もちろん篝も一緒に…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:01.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,篝？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:06.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,今日はなんだか静かですね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なんだ　いまの音は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:15.68,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,うそ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,どうしたんだ　小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.51,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,結界が外から壊されたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:20.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:33.59,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,よ　やっぱりいたかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.39,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,おまえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,お友たちのガーディアンも一緒か
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:42.57,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,それとももうくたばっちまったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.61,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,おまえがルチアを…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:48.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,腹に串ぶっ刺してバーベキューにしてやったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,いい焼き加減だったろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:51.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,てめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:56.69,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,おいおい　そんな隠し玉持ってやがったのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ならオレも見せてやらなきゃなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:01.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なに　地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:04.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,おまえらカス程度にゃもったいねえが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:07.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,その力存分に味わいやがれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.23,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ちびもす　みんな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:28.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,うーんと頑張る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.77,0:04:41.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,魔物使いもいやがるのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.11,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なんですか　この魔物は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:50.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,よ　やっぱり生きていたか　狩猟者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.11,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,今度はちゃんと殺してやるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ちびもす　お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なにをする？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:03.07,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,逃げるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:06.51,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あんな魔物　そう長いこと使役できるはずない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.39,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,それに…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.55,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ここはもう…お仕舞いだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:15.01,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.93,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そうですわ　早く逃げましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あいつやべーよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.05,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そうは言ってもな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:27.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.25,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,とっておきが来るから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.49,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,銃だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,始末しろ　デカ物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:46.89,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:55.07,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,行こう　今のうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,待てよ　なんでここに圭介さんと理香子さん…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.65,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,小鳥の両親がいるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:03.01,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,さあ　早く
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:03.73,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,待てよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.39,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,小鳥　オレの話を…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あれはただの魔物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,誰が逃がすかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:19.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,わたし　難しいことはぜんぜんわかりませんけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:22.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,いまは逃げなきゃだめだと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:23.49,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,わかった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,これがあれば家族を守れる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ええ　そうね　あなた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,行きましょう　あなた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:39.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.49,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そんな…ありえないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,だって　二人はもう…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:49.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,お父さん　お母さん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:52.66,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,邪魔するんじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,わたしがとしたことが　離れすぎましたね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:04.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ちはやさん　どうかご無事で
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:14.65,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ミドウの邪魔はさせない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:23.85,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ガイア最強　その力果たして噂通りのものか　試させてもらうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,キリマンジャロに　クリボイログですか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:29.47,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,わたしを相手にするには
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,少々役不足かと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.77,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,雑魚が手間をかけさせやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:56.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,頼むぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:57.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,おう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.25,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,バイアーン帯剣緑地騎士団
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:03.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,出るぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,それじゃ　わたしも出るから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:11.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,っと　その前に一つはっきりさせておきたいんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:16.38,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ルチアちゃんもあなたも　バカなことを考えてないでしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:21.61,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ならいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:26.53,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　静流ちゃんはいい子でお留守番ね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.99,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,いざというときの切り札なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:33.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,忘れないでね　あなたはガーディアンなのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.39,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,十年前のあの日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ドルイドになったあたしが　最初に作った魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:59.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,それが　お父さんとお母さんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:03.79,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,動くし　喋りもする
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:08.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,でもそれは　生きてた頃の反射行動でしかなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:11.41,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そんなの　もうただの道具だから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:15.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,最後まで便利に…使った…だけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:19.91,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ごめんな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,一緒にいたのに　気づいてやれなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:30.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,それどころか　事故のことすらオレは覚えてさえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:35.95,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,いいの　瑚太朗くんがあたしに謝ることなんて　何一つないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:37.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:43.89,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,みんな無事か
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,はい　こっちは平気です
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,てめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:52.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,先に行け
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:54.53,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,オレがこいつを止める
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,バカな　なにを言ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:58.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,一人なんて無理ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:09:58.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:01.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あとで必ず合流する
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.75,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,嘘ついちゃいやだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:03.97,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,わかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:09.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,他人のために我が身を犠牲にか　感動的だな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.27,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,反吐が出るほどによ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:14.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,篝には　指一本触れさせねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:16.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,篝？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:18.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ああ　鍵のことか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:23.20,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そうだな　狩猟者どもなら眼の色を変えるだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:26.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,オレが殺したいのはてめえだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:33.61,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なんで　オレなんかに　そんなに拘るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.23,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,てめえだけじゃねえさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:39.67,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,生ぬるい世界で毎日毎日ヘラヘラしてるこの国のクソども
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:43.07,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,一匹残らず塵にしたいだけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:55.68,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,痛えだろ　平和ボケの甘ちゃんには耐えられねえよな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:58.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あいつやられちゃうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:03.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あの方　あんな強力な魔物を二台も従えて　なんでまだ生きてますの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.01,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,痛えよ　けどな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:12.49,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あいにく痛みだけは　咲夜の野郎に散々教わってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.77,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,このガキが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.59,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,大当たり　ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:35.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,チッ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:38.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なるほど　こいつは化け物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ひよっこどもじゃ相手にならねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,狩猟者の増援か
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:45.47,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あれって…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:49.61,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,まさかおっさんたち…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:51.47,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,坊主？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:52.99,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,源さん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:57.61,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あれが恐らく鍵だ　なぜ我らにも見えるのかはわからんが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:12:00.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なぁに　見えるなら壊しやすいわい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:03.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,させるか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,すまねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.47,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,鍵をつれてさっさと失せろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:22.11,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,な…なんでおまえが俺たちを…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:26.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,くっそが　あんなくだらねえ約束すんじゃなかったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:29.37,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,全部焼き尽くしてやるよ　狩猟者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,は…早く行こうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.93,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,今のうちですわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:42.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ずいぶんと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:50.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,好き勝手してくれたもんだな　ガイアよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:54.20,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,てめえらが言うかよ　狩猟者が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:57.29,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,おらおら　どうした　どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.20,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,世界はいつだってそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:10.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,弱いやつから何もかも奪ってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,だから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.67,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ぶっ壊してやるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:27.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ちっ　限界か
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:41.19,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,だめよ　ミドウ　みんなと仲良くしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.47,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そいつがおっちょこちょいなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:45.47,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,もう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,見たかったな…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:14.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,クソったれな世界がぶっ壊れるところをよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:23.68,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,済まねえ　鍵は取り逃がしちまった　でだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:27.87,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,鍵と一緒にいったのは例の要注意対象だったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.53,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,わかった　そのまま連中の追撃を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:37.27,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,天王寺　貴様は…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:53.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そいつは生かしておけば　世界をぶっ壊す存在だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:58.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,大事に大事に守ったその果てに　絶望しやがれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:02.25,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,篝　救済ってなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,おまえが探してる自分ってなんなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:10.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,おい　しっかりしろよ　おまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:13.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,もう　体がボロボロなんですわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,やべー　追いつかれた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,来ないでくださいまし
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.87,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,いっぱいいっぱい考えた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.47,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,これが正しいのかわからない　でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:35.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なんで　ここに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,私はオカ研の仲間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.03,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,し…ず…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:49.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,静流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:52.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,いったたた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,夢だったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:55.63,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,夢じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.55,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,おはよう　瑚太朗君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,意外と早起きだ　瑚太朗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:06.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そうか　来てくれたんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:10.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,静流が瑚太朗とルチアの傷を治してくれたんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:11.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.43,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,サンキューな　静流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:15.93,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ここなら　今のところは安全だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:16.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ここ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:17.78,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,えー　なんなんだ　ここは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.85,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,石の町という　ガイアの施設らしい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:27.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,えっと　ガイアの術でこの世界の裏側に
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:30.78,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,もう一つの世界を作ったみたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,魔物置き場とかで使われてるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:38.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,場所はうろ覚えだったんですけど　なんとかここへ逃げ込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,それで篝は？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:44.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,今朝からずっとあの調子のままですね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:56.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なぜこうまでしてあなたは　人を滅ぼそうとするんです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:04.43,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,代々　聖女の魂と記憶は後継者に転写されていく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.63,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,今はまだ呑まれていないようだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,おまえにもすでに刻まれているはず
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:14.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,聖女が人間に絶望したせいだと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:18.99,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,世代を重ねることに研ぎ澄まされ純化した絶望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:24.65,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,私たちの中にそれを覆すよい記憶など　一つもありはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:27.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,私には　あります
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.79,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,戯れに通わせたあのおままごとのことかい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:35.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,では　抗ってみるといいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:38.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,私からおまえ　おまえからしまこ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:42.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,この連綿と続く聖女たちの絶望に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:46.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,下準備は上々　頃合いね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:51.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,歌を響かせるためにも　鍵を現世に引きずり出す
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:52.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,では…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:56.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,観測者の木が出現した後　聖歌隊を神殿へ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.10,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,私もこれから向かうわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.63,0:18:00.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,私も行きます
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:03.91,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,好きになさい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:09.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,お手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:11.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,鼻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.49,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なんかすげえ懐かしい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:18.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あとはここに　あの人さえいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:19.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,会長さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:24.55,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,おい　篝　今日は黙りがすぎるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ヒーコー切れか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ホントは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:32.35,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ホントは気づいてるんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:36.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,これが本当の篝　生き物なんかじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:40.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,救済を起こすだけの　人間の形をしたただの現象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:43.47,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,魔物と　変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:48.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,でも　ついこの間まで　勝手なことばかり言って　人を困らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:51.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,まずいコーヒーを　うまいうまいって喜んでさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:52.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,瑚太朗君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.53,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ダメだった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:56.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,篝？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:00.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ダメだった　見付からなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.39,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,見つけなれないって　何を？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:10.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,人の織りなす　よい記憶を　私は　見つけられなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:15.39,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,どういうつもりだ　加島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:19.79,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,すべての魔物使いに　町への出撃命令を出すなどと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,戦争でも始める気か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:27.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,いいえ　終わらせるのよ　すべてを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.61,0:19:29.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,待て　どこ行く
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:33.91,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,最後の時を迎えるにふさわしい場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:36.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,貴様　もしや鍵を…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:40.73,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,やめろ　鍵は滅びを管理するための道具でなければならない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,真の滅びなど　誰が望む
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,さ…くら…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,本物の絶望を知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:20:00.66,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ただ人生にふてくされただけのものなど煩わしいばかりね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:14.30,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,さあ　鍵よ　こちらへ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:23.20,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,篝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,突然篝に何が？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:30.27,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,どうした　ちー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.70,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,えっと　何か聞こえません？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,何かって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.05,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,たぶん歌みたいな何か
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,そうです　これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.93,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:44.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,木が…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:46.83,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あれはなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:51.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:07.07,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,少々敵を侮りすぎましたか　早くちはやさんの元へ戻らねば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:24.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.19,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,すごい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:29.83,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,デカい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:30.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:32.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,一体どうなってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:34.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,おい　なんだあれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:35.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なんかやばくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.97,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ここは　風祭か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:44.27,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,誰かが石の町から　私たちごと風祭に召喚したんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:49.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,どうしただ　急に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:51.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,魔物だ　瑚太朗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:56.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,バカな　一般人の目の前で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,あ…あれを見てください
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:03.09,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,今度はなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:03.93,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,なっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:06.09,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,森が…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:08.03,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,広がっていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:17.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,ついに始まってしまったの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:21.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,今こそ救済の時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:28.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B - D,,0,0,0,,人間よ　おまえたちによき終末が訪れんことを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:10.25,OP JP EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}少しずつ波紋は離れていった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:15.49,OP JP EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}いつしか　ひとつも重ならなくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:23.19,OP JP EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}それでもいい　きみと居たら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:31.64,OP JP EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}こんな気持ち　いつから抱いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:41.93,OP JP EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}ただひとりの少年の恋物語だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.92,0:01:47.84,OP JP EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}永遠にきみを守ってみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:53.00,OP JP EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}この胸に　刻み込む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:58.36,OP JP EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}いつから　ふたりきりになったんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:03.81,OP JP EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}もういいか　そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:12.36,OP JP EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}笑ってよ　終わるその日には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:38.83,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}懐かしさも消えた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:46.74,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}迷い子の手が寂しく　風を撫でた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:54.46,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}言葉を知らないままならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:59.17,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}この瞳を閉じることも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:03.49,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}簡単だったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:10.46,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}初めて触れた温もり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:15.99,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}小さく芽吹く鼓動に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.23,0:23:21.29,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}戸惑いを覚えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:28.17,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}あなたの声探して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:32.01,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}夢幻の道を行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:36.01,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}星の始まりを識る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:39.32,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}ただそれたけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.72,0:23:43.67,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}口に残る苦みも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:47.53,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}記憶の鍵になる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:51.39,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}いつか出会うあなたへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.39,0:23:56.70,JP_ED EPSON 太明朝体Ｂ-右下,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(200,200)}最後に微笑みを
